en_172375_0	The Criminal Investigation Department has launched a criminal investigation into Treasury bond issuances took place during the term of former Central bank Governor Arjuna Mahendran.
en_172375_1	Deputy Solicitor General, Dappula de Livera informed the Presidential Commission of Inquiry probing the controversial bond issuance today (02) when it began proceedings after a week's break.
en_172375_2	Mahendran has been testified before the Commission from this morning.
